47
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:47,070
Now convolution, as an algebraic
operation, has a

48
00:03:47,070 --> 00:03:51,000
number of important
properties.

49
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:55,370
One of the properties of
convolution is that it is what

50
00:03:55,370 --> 00:03:58,300
