continuous time.

56
00:04:23,990 --> 00:04:28,050
And it says, as I just
indicated, that x[n]

57
00:04:28,050 --> 00:04:30,240
convolved with h[n]

58
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:32,500
is equal to h[n]

59
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,750
convolved with x[n].

60
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:38,930
Or the same, of course,
in continuous time.

61
00:04:38,930 --> 00:04:44,200
And in fact, in the lecture
last time, we worked an

62
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:48,000
example where we had, in
